description:
Visit: http://COVERTACTIONMAGAZINE.COM
Lou Wolf, one of the founders of Covert Action Information Bulletin along with Philip Agee, James and Elsie Wilcott, and Ellen Ray and Bill Schaap, talks about the magazine's relaunch, the history of CAIB, Gina Haspel, Obama, Trump and more.

For more related content, please visit: https://ourhiddenhistory.org and https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
